These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
City: boston, colone
Hobby: drawing, dancing
Job: lawyer, teacher
1. Hobby:drawing is on the right of Job:lawyer##1
2. City:colone is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| City   | colone    | boston |
| Hobby         | dancing | drawing    |
| Job     | lawyer     | teacher      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
Birthday: june, december
Flower: azalea, daisy
Job: writer, librarian
1. Job:librarian is on the left of Birthday:june##1
2. Flower:azalea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Birthday      | december  | june   |
| Flower   | daisy | azalea  |
| Job     | librarian   | writer |

