.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
Birthday: april, may
Flower: sunflower, marigold
House: cape-cod, townhouse
1. House:townhouse is on the left of Flower:sunflower##1
2. House:cape-cod is on the left or right of House:townhouse##3
3. Birthday:april is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Birthday    | may | april     |
| Flower     | marigold | sunflower |
| House   | townhouse | cape-cod    |

